* MooseFS 1.7.26 (2014-03-05)

  - (master+mount) create file using one command

* MooseFS 1.7.25 (2014-02-27)

  - (all) fixed another bug in new network module (introduced in 1.7.21 and 1.7.22)
  - (cs) new I/O model
